OL,4,CPC Harper's widow vows to continue push
OL,5,Cfor law change
OL,6, PC Andrew Harper's widow has vowed to
OL,7, continue her bid to get the law changed
OL,8, on the anniversary of launching her
OL,9, Harper's Law campaign.
OL,11,FPC Harper was dragged to his death by a
OL,12,Fgetaway car in August 2019. Three
OL,13,Fteenagers were jailed for between 13
OL,14,Fand 16 years for his manslaughter.
OL,16,FLissie Harper wants life sentences for
OL,17,Fpeople who kill emergency workers.
OL,19,FShe said she would pursue the change
OL,20,F"until Harper's Law is written in the
OL,21,Fhistory books".
